{"tid":532111,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"同車男女相約啪啪啪　竟都背著另一半偷來","createTime":"2018-01-17T13:13:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-17T13:24:48.000Z","uid":167280,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7ec9423e5bc763ef307d90bf7b64a2276257499c","tid":532111,"uid":167280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T13:13:21.000Z","msg":"台南市一對吸毒男女昨天相約要到某廉價旅館做愛，轎車行經中正派出所後方道路，中正派出所警員邱漢文、陳明杰、張至綱巡邏經過，發現兩人神情詭異，趨前攔查時，乘客曾女開車門想跑，警方隨即攔查。警方在曾女身上查獲3小包2.63公克海洛因，並確認兩人是吸毒人口，全案依毒品防制條例送辦。<br />\n警方調查，章男（56歲）、曾女（40歲）是吸毒認識的一般朋友，<span style=\"color: red;\"> 他們各有男女朋友</span>，兩人昨天下午要到中西區某廉價旅館吸毒做愛。章男開著黑色轎車行經中正派出所後方的金華新路，資深警員邱漢文發現轎車在找路，停停走走，隨即率同車陳明杰、張至綱鳴警報器，攔下轎車。<br />\n當轎車停下，坐在副駕駛座的曾女隨即拿著皮包開門往外衝，張至綱一手抓住對方。警方調閱兩人身分資料，發現他們都是毒品人口，果然在曾女皮包內查獲一級毒品海洛因3小包重2.63公克。<br />\n警方指出，章男住在北區，曾女則是麻豆人，2人相約要到中西區的廉價旅館施用毒品及嘿咻，不料才剛到市區，就被眼尖的員警查獲，毒品也被扣案。警方依毒品危害防制條例將持有毒品的曾女送辦。<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20180117/1280217\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20180117%2F1280217&d=WGx0PWGxoukb3bVjM6YW8MmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=06b39ca5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20180117%2F1280217&h=8a71a467\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20180117/1280217</a>"},{"pid":"4c87ebe432c24aa59dedf2abd8e6ae5d03adc481","tid":532111,"uid":167280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T13:15:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1150c1daee05235c5d2568541a9e693d4c717e4f","tid":532111,"uid":167280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T13:20:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a1a20896e3f47a730761586a6956f21d70ebfd1","tid":532111,"uid":127716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T13:24:48.000Z","msg":"台狗真係好鍾意吸毒扑野打孖黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}